pure-gen (0.21-2) cosmic; urgency=medium

  * Work around Launchpad issues with the maintainer-build target. We
    don't have a working internet connection there, so the 2.x version of
    cabal-install won't work, and we have to directly invoke
    language-c/Setup.hs instead.

 -- Albert Graef <aggraef@gmail.com>  Mon, 29 Oct 2018 21:35:58 +0100

