pure-gen (0.17-2) trusty; urgency=low

  * Upstream bugfix: pure-gen dumps core on illegal instruction, depending
    on the build host's cpu type. Prevent this by passing the
    -mcpu=generic option to llc when batch-compiling the script.

 -- Albert Graef <aggraef@gmail.com>  Mon, 15 Sep 2014 00:31:44 +0200

